Class RequestCmdData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ly15_qz18.model.data.RequestCmdData

    public class RequestCmdData
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRequestCmdType
    When a receiver found it missing a command, it will send a data packet with RequestCmdData inside to the sender to request a command.
